This project exists to generate revenue and validate a future SaaS.

Target:
Recruiters and small recruiting agencies doing outreach.

Core problem:
- Low reply rates
- Time wasted on manual outreach
- Inconsistent follow-ups

Core outcome:
- More replies
- More booked meetings
- Less manual work

Current focus (Phase 1 - Validation):
- Build simple outreach system
- Test on real recruiters
- Close 1–3 paying clients
- Measure reply rate improvement

What we are NOT doing:
- Building SaaS yet
- Creating dashboards
- Over-engineering systems

What defines success:
- Recruiter pays for system
- Outreach generates replies
- At least 1 measurable improvement

Next step after validation:
- Identify patterns
- Turn repeated workflows into SaaS features